'''(1685) 托羅'''是一顆與[[地球|地球]]以8：5和與[[金星|金星]]以13：5[[軌道共振|共振]]軌道環繞太陽的[[阿波羅型小行星|阿波羅型小行星]]。由於這種不尋常的軌道，它有時也被稱為'''地球的第二顆[[衛星|衛星]]'''<ref>{{cite web | author=Bruce Duensing | title=Ruminations On An Asteroid Named 1685 Toro | url=http://materialintangible.blogspot.com/2009/02/ruminations-on-asteroid-named-1685-toro.html | work=Intangible Materiality | date=2009-02-16| accessdate=4 August 2011 | archive-date=2012-09-29 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B2MwKgGn?url=http://materialintangible.blogspot.com/2009/02/ruminations-on-asteroid-named-1685-toro.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

托羅是在1948年被[[卡爾·A.維他南|卡爾·A.維他南]]在[[利克天文台|利克天文台]]發現的<ref name="NYTimes1948b">{{cite newspaper | newspaper=The New York Times | url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F00F1EFE3F5E167B93C4AB1789D95F4C8485F9 | date=December 26, 1948 | title=Science in Review: Research Work in Astronomy and Cancer Lead Year's List of Scientific Developments | author=Waldemar Kaempffert | page=87 | issn=1494850 | accessdate=4 August 2011 | archive-date=2012-09-29 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6B2Mvo0Ri?url=http://select.nytimes.com/gst/abstract.html?res=F00F1EFE3F5E167B93C4AB1789D95F4C8485F9 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。它是被發現的第三顆[[阿波羅型小行星|阿波羅型小行星]]，名稱是用來向天文學家[[Samuel_Herrick_(astronomer)|Samuel Herrick]].的妻子，拜突利亞·托羅表達敬意。  Herrick曾經研究這顆小行星的軌道，並且要求繼[[小行星1580|(1580) 拜突利亞]]之後採用這個名字<ref>{{cite book | last=Schmadel | first=Lutz D. | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=uwGbkbhMVyAC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Dictionary of Minor Planet Names: Addendum to Fifth Edition: 2006-2008 | location=Berlin | publisher=Springer Berlin | year=2009 | isbn=9783642019647 | accessdate=4 August 2011 | archive-date=2013-12-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231224639/http://books.google.com/books?id=uwGbkbhMVyAC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_v2_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>University of California, [http://content.cdlib.org/view?docId=hb9k4009c7;NAAN=13030&doc.view=frames&chunk.id=div00024&toc.depth=1&toc.id=&brand=calisphere Samuel Herrick, Engineering; Astronomy: Los Angeles] {{Wayback|url=http://content.cdlib.org/view?docId=hb9k4009c7;NAAN=13030&doc.view=frames&chunk.id=div00024&toc.depth=1&toc.id=&brand=calisphere |date=20181122135737 }}</ref>。

依據軌道路徑，(1685) 托羅是[[夕拉科加隕石|夕拉科加隕石]]來源的最佳候選者，這是所知唯一一顆曾經擊傷人的隕石，它於1954年11月30日在[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]]的[[夕拉科加|夕拉科加]]擊傷婦人安·霍奇斯<ref name=povenmire>[http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu//full/1995LPI....26.1133P/0001133.000.html?high=484678bbd531063 H. Povenmire. ''The Sylacauga, Alabama Meteorite: The Impact Locations, Atmosphere Trajectory, Strewn Field and Radiant''] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.adsabs.harvard.edu//full/1995LPI....26.1133P/0001133.000.html?high=484678bbd531063 |date=20200513185032 }}. H.Povenmire. Abstracts of the Lunar and Planetary Science Conference, volume 26, page 1133, (1995)</ref>。

